# YouTube Channel Filter

**Powerful YouTube video filter — block channels, filter by keyword, duration, language, live streams and members-only content.**

---

## ✨ Features

### 🚫 Channel Blocklist
- Add channels to a blocklist to hide all their videos across every page
- Individual channel removal with inline confirmation (no popup dialogs)
- Bulk clear all
- **Tag system**: assign custom tags (e.g. "News", "Gaming") to organize blocked channels, with tag-based filtering in the management panel

### ⭐ Whitelist
- Whitelist channels are **completely protected** — no filter rule of any kind will hide them
- Individual removal with confirmation
- Bulk clear all

### 🔤 Keyword Filters
- Create multiple keyword groups, each with its own enable/disable toggle
- Match against video **title** and/or **description**
- Supports plain text and **Regular Expressions** (Regex)
- Example regex: `^\[AD\]` hides all videos whose title starts with "[AD]"

### ⚙️ Advanced Filters
- **Video duration**: hide videos shorter/longer than specified seconds
- **Live streams**: hide currently live videos
- **Upcoming premieres**: hide scheduled premiere videos
- **Members-only**: hide videos behind a paid membership
- **Language filter**: auto-detect language from title characters; supports 16 preset languages + custom BCP-47 codes
- **Whitelist-only mode**: show only whitelisted channels, hide everything else

### 📊 Statistics & History
- Total hidden video count with keyword and channel hit rankings (bar chart)
- History log of up to 500 hidden videos with timestamp and filter reason
- One-click reset

### 💾 Export / Import
- Full settings JSON backup/restore (merge or overwrite mode)
- Blocklist, whitelist, keyword CSV export/import
- **Share filter lists**: generate a URL to share your blocklist/whitelist/keywords with others; recipients are prompted to import on first visit

### 🖱️ Quick Action Buttons
- **Homepage / Search / Subscriptions**: hover over any video card → a translucent action bar slides up from the bottom of the thumbnail with 🚫 / ⭐ buttons
- **Sidebar recommendations** (watch page): hover over a card → small circular 🚫 / ⭐ icons appear in the top-right corner of the thumbnail
- **Channel pages**: a "Block this channel / Add to whitelist" button bar appears in the channel header

### 🔘 Top Bar Button
- Injected next to the YouTube avatar button
- **Left-click**: open/close management panel
- **Right-click**: toggle filter on/off (pause/resume)

### ⏰ Auto Backup
- Automatically exports a backup JSON on a configurable schedule (daily to monthly)
- Optional filename prefix (e.g. `mybackup` → `mybackup-20250410.json`)
- Without a prefix, always overwrites `yt-filter-backup.json` — ideal for a fixed backup slot

